title: Jason's Deli
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, American, Salad bar, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Chain deli with a salad bar with a reasonable amount of vegetables and vegan toppings, including red pepper hummus, nuts, seeds, olives, beans. Has a vegetarian and vegan menu, at least one vegan soup, and a few of the sandwiches/wraps can be made vegan. Casual atmosphere, very popular and gets busy at peak times.
